  "name": "North Wind's Night Verse",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>This <em>+1 striking frost katana</em> is always cool to the touch, nearly uncomfortably so. Unadorned and with no tsuba, its honed blade is carved from a single tusk of dragon-turtle ivory and wrapped in strips of winter wolf hide. Strikes with the katana gain a +2 status bonus to damage rolls against creatures that have a status penalty to their Speed or are slowed. The status bonus increases to +3 if the weapon has a greater striking rune and +4 for major striking.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">f</span> command (cold, evocation, magical)</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per 1 minute</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> Your spell deals cold damage to a creature</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> Choose one creature dealt cold damage by the spell. It takes a -5-foot status penalty to its Speeds for 1 round.</p>"
    },
